msgid ""
"Now you are ready to play your first round of <literal>Go</literal>. If you "
"are not familiar with the rules, we recommend reading the corresponding "
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Go_(game)\">Wikipedia article</"
"ulink> or take <ulink url=\"http://playgo.to/iwtg/en/\">The Interactive Way "
